        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"deepseek/deepseek-chat\",\n  \"max_tokens\": 1000,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": {{ \n        JSON.stringify(\n`คุณคือ marketing expert\n\nBrand:\n${$items(\"analyze brand\")[0].json.keywords}\n\nInfluencer:\nTitle: ${$json.title}\nNickname: ${$json.nickname}\nAvatar: ${$json.Avatar}\nTikTok Profile: ${$json.Tikokt_Profile}\nFollowers: ${$json.followers}\nEngagement: ${$json.engagement}\n\nให้คะแนนความเข้ากัน 0-100\n\nตอบกลับ JSON เท่านั้น:\n{\n  \"Avater\": \"\",\n  \"Tiktok_Profile\": \"\",\n  \"nickname\": \"\",\n  \"score\": 0,\n  \"reason\": \"\"\n}`\n        ) \n      }}\n    }\n  ]\n}",
